com.taobao.datax.common.util
类 DbWriterProxy

java.lang.Object
  com.taobao.datax.common.util.DbWriterProxy

public class DbWriterProxy
extends java.lang.Object

A proxy which provides to database Writer plugin. Usually this proxy is held by a Writer plugin. The proxy depends on jdbc service and write data to data destinamtion.

另请参见：
Reader, DbWriterProxy

receiverFromReader

public void receiverFromReader(LineReceiver receiver,
                               java.sql.Connection conn,
                               MetaData meta)
                        throws java.sql.SQLException
Get data from Reader. This method makeups sql sentence throws a String Pattern , and data in type of Line from LineReceiver, then execute sql sentence by param Statement.

参数：
receiver - a LineReceiver.
INSERT_PATTERN - format of sql sentence.
stmt - a Statement.
meta - a .
b - True if sql pattern like: insert into tableName values {0}.
False if sql pattern like: insert into tableName {0} values {1}.
抛出：
java.sql.SQLException - if occurs SQLException.
